### Register (p√∫blico)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

# Body: incluir roles (USER/ADMIN), password de 8+ caracteres; isActive es opcional (default true)

{
  "username": "nuevo",
  "email": "nuevo@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "roles": ["USER", "ADMIN"],
  "isActive": true
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "nuevo",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": false
}

# Copiar el "accessToken" de la respuesta y usalo en el header:
# Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>

### Ver mi perfil privado (requiere token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
